---

---

<section class="py-24 bg-surface-dark border-t border-b border-border-dark relative z-10">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mb-20 text-center relative">
      <span class="text-primary font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase mb-3 block">
        Diagnóstico
      </span>
      <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-white font-display mb-4">
        Por qué tu tráfico <br /> no se convierte en dinero
      </h2>
      <p class="text-text-dim text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto font-light">
        El 90% de los negocios pierden ventas por usar plantillas genéricas. Estos son los "asesinos de conversión" más comunes.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Scroll Stacking Container -->
    <div class="relative w-full pb-32">
      <!-- Card 1 -->
      <div class="sticky top-24 pt-8 transition-transform duration-500 will-change-transform">
        <div class="bg-background-dark border border-border-dark p-8 md:p-12 rounded-sm shadow-2xl relative overflow-hidden group min-h-[45vh] flex flex-col justify-center">
          <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-1 h-full bg-red-500"></div>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
            
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-red-500/10 flex items-center justify-center border border-red-500/20">
                <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-red-500">1</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Tiempos de carga que matan ventas</h3>
                <p class="text-text-dim text-lg leading-relaxed">
                  Tus prospectos no tienen paciencia. <strong class="text-white font-normal">Por cada segundo extra de carga, la conversión cae un 12%.</strong> Si usas WordPress con decenas de plugins, estás regalando clientes a tu competencia.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="h-64 bg-surface-dark border border-border-dark/50 rounded-sm relative overflow-hidden flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-6">
              <span class="text-text-dim text-sm mb-4 font-mono">Performance Metric</span>
              <!-- Loading visual -->
              <div class="w-full max-w-sm bg-background-dark h-4 rounded-full overflow-hidden border border-border-dark relative">
                <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 h-full bg-red-500 w-full translate-x-[-80%] group-hover:translate-x-[-10%] transition-transform duration-[3000ms] ease-out"></div>
              </div>
              <div class="mt-6 flex justify-between w-full max-w-sm text-sm font-mono opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity delay-1000 duration-500">
                <span class="text-red-400">Time: 4.2s (Poor)</span>
                <span class="text-red-500 font-bold">Conv: -50.4%</span>
              </div>
              <!-- Glitch overlay on hover -->
              <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-red-500/5 mix-blend-overlay opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300 pointer-events-none"></div>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 2 -->
      <div class="sticky top-32 pt-8 transition-transform duration-500 will-change-transform" style="z-index: 2;">
        <div class="bg-background-dark border border-border-dark p-8 md:p-12 rounded-sm shadow-2xl relative overflow-hidden group min-h-[45vh] flex flex-col justify-center">
          <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-1 h-full bg-orange-500"></div>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
            
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-orange-500/10 flex items-center justify-center border border-orange-500/20">
                <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-orange-500">2</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Diseño Plantillero "Bonito" pero Inútil</h3>
                <p class="text-text-dim text-lg leading-relaxed">
                  Una landing no es un cuadro expositivo, es un <strong class="text-white font-normal">vendedor digital</strong>. Las plantillas prefabricadas distraen al usuario del objetivo principal: hacer clic en tu botón de compra o agenda.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="h-64 bg-surface-dark border border-border-dark/50 rounded-sm relative overflow-hidden flex items-center justify-center p-6 gap-4">
              <!-- Generic wireframes stacking -->
              <div class="w-32 h-40 border border-border-dark bg-background-dark rounded-sm absolute left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-4 shadow-xl opacity-50 group-hover:-translate-y-8 group-hover:-rotate-6 transition-all duration-700">
                <div class="h-8 bg-surface-dark m-2 border border-border-dark/50"></div>
                <div class="h-4 bg-surface-dark m-2 w-1/2 border border-border-dark/50"></div>
              </div>
              <div class="w-32 h-40 border border-border-dark bg-background-dark rounded-sm absolute left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 shadow-xl opacity-75 group-hover:translate-x-[20%] group-hover:rotate-6 transition-all duration-700">
                <div class="h-8 bg-surface-dark m-2 border border-border-dark/50"></div>
                <div class="h-4 bg-surface-dark m-2 w-2/3 border border-border-dark/50"></div>
              </div>
              <div class="w-32 h-40 border border-orange-500/50 bg-background-dark rounded-sm absolute left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 translate-y-4 shadow-xl group-hover:translate-y-8 transition-all duration-700 flex flex-col">
                <div class="h-8 bg-orange-500/20 m-2 border border-orange-500/30 flex items-center justify-center"><span class="text-[8px] text-orange-500 font-mono">TEMPLATE</span></div>
                <div class="h-4 bg-surface-dark m-2 w-3/4 border border-border-dark/50"></div>
                <div class="h-10 bg-surface-dark mx-2 border border-border-dark/50"></div>
              </div>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 3 -->
      <div class="sticky top-40 pt-8 transition-transform duration-500 will-change-transform" style="z-index: 3;">
        <div class="bg-background-dark border border-border-dark p-8 md:p-12 rounded-sm shadow-2xl relative overflow-hidden group min-h-[45vh] flex flex-col justify-center">
          <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-1 h-full bg-yellow-500"></div>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
            
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-yellow-500/10 flex items-center justify-center border border-yellow-500/20">
                <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-yellow-500">3</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Falta de Autoridad Visual</h3>
                <p class="text-text-dim text-lg leading-relaxed">
                  Cobras miles de dólares por tu servicio, pero tu web parece hecha con $50. Un diseño premium y a medida activa el <strong class="text-white font-normal">gatillo mental de autoridad</strong> instantáneamente.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="h-64 bg-surface-dark border border-border-dark/50 rounded-sm relative overflow-hidden flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-6 p-6">
              <!-- Trust comparison -->
              <div class="w-full flex justify-between items-center gap-4">
                <div class="flex-1 border border-border-dark bg-background-dark p-4 rounded-sm opacity-50 filter grayscale group-hover:opacity-30 transition-all duration-500 text-center">
                  <span class="text-xl">🥉</span>
                  <div class="h-2 w-16 bg-border-dark mx-auto mt-2 rounded"></div>
                </div>
                <span class="text-text-dim text-xs font-mono">VS</span>
                <div class="flex-1 border border-yellow-500/30 bg-yellow-500/5 p-4 rounded-sm scale-100 group-hover:scale-110 shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(234,179,8,0.1)] transition-all duration-500 text-center relative overflow-hidden">
                  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-tr from-transparent via-white/5 to-transparent translate-x-[-100%] group-hover:translate-x-[100%] transition-transform duration-1000 ease-in-out"></div>
                  <span class="text-2xl drop-shadow-[0_0_8px_rgba(234,179,8,0.5)]">✨</span>
                  <div class="h-2 w-16 bg-yellow-500/50 mx-auto mt-2 rounded"></div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p class="text-xs text-text-dim font-mono tracking-widest uppercase">Percepción de Valor</p>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 4 -->
      <div class="sticky top-48 pt-8 transition-transform duration-500 will-change-transform" style="z-index: 4;">
        <div class="bg-background-dark border border-border-dark p-8 md:p-12 rounded-sm shadow-2xl relative overflow-hidden group min-h-[45vh] flex flex-col justify-center">
          <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-1 h-full bg-primary"></div>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
            
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center border border-primary/20">
                <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary">4</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Copywriting sin Fricción (El Filtro)</h3>
                <p class="text-text-dim text-lg leading-relaxed">
                  Inviertes en anuncios, pero el tráfico llega a un "colador". Una estructura persuasiva lleva a tu cliente ideal <strong class="text-white font-normal">desde el dolor hasta el deseo obsesivo</strong> de trabajar contigo.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="h-64 bg-surface-dark border border-border-dark/50 rounded-sm relative overflow-hidden flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-6">
              <!-- Funnel animation -->
              <div class="relative w-32 flex flex-col items-center">
                <div class="w-full h-8 border-t-2 border-x-2 border-border-dark border-dashed flex justify-center items-start rounded-t-sm">
                   <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-text-dim mt-1 group-hover:translate-y-24 group-hover:bg-primary transition-all duration-[1.5s] ease-in"></div>
                   <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-text-dim mt-1 mx-2 group-hover:translate-x-12 group-hover:opacity-0 transition-all duration-700 ease-out"></div>
                   <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-text-dim mt-1 group-hover:-translate-x-12 group-hover:opacity-0 transition-all duration-500 ease-out"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="w-2/3 h-8 border-x-2 border-border-dark border-dashed"></div>
                <div class="w-1/3 h-12 border-x-2 border-b-2 border-primary border-solid rounded-b-sm bg-primary/5 flex items-end justify-center pb-2 relative overflow-hidden">
                  <div class="absolute bottom-0 w-full bg-primary/20 h-0 group-hover:h-full transition-all duration-[2s] delay-500"></div>
                  <span class="text-primary text-xs font-bold z-10 shrink-0">$</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <span class="text-text-dim text-xs font-mono mt-4 uppercase tracking-widest">Embudo Optimizado</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
